          "process_md": "> **Registration Process:**\n\n**Step-1:** Visit the [Investor Facilitation Portal (IFP)](https://ifp.gujarat.gov.in/DIGIGOV/) portal. Click on &quot;New Investor Registration&quot; to access the registration form.\n**Step-2:** Fill in the Registration Form. Click on &quot;Submit&quot;. \n**Step-3:** Verify the E-mail ID using the link sent on your registered E-mail ID.\n**Step-4:** After verification, you will be registered successfully.\n<br>\n\n> **Post-Registration Process:**\n\n**Step-1:** Visit the [Investor Facilitation Portal (IFP)](https://ifp.gujarat.gov.in/DIGIGOV/) portal. Click on &quot;Login&quot;.\n**Step-2:** Enter the email address and password you used during registration.\n**Step-3:** Click the &quot;Login&quot; button to access your account.\n**Step-4:** Now fill in the required details and mandatory documents about your business to complete the application process.\n<br>\n\n> **Helpdesk:** [**Contact Here.**](https://ifp.gujarat.gov.in/DIGIGOV/IFP-pages/contact.jsp?pagedisp=static)\n\n"
        }
